Ny RBK-nedtur: Sesongen over for sommerens store formspiller
01 Nov 2019, 20:53 by Ole K. Sagbakken,Anne-Marit Dahl
Anders Konradsen (29) blir ikke kvitt akilles-plagene. Tirsdag blir det operasjon. I begge beina.

STRØMSGODSET - ROSENBORG 3–3

New RBK downturn: The season for this summer's great form player
01 Nov 2019, 20:53 by Ole K. Sagbakken, Anne-Marit Dahl
Anders Konradsen (29) does not get rid of the Achilles tendon. Tuesday will be surgery. In both legs.

POWER GOODS - ROSENBORG 3–3
